Poem - Pain refers to text at https://raw.githubusercontent.com/vinu1A23/poems/main/Poem%20-%20Pain

Pain leaves none
paints the inner one
pointing to all but one
preparing for the dreadful hum
preaching lessons to some
pain leaves none
